<section sectnbr = "3D">
<servcat sctnbr = "03" scnbr = "04">
<configtype typenbr = "0">
<servinfotype sitcode = "6">
<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A3406002" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Propeller Shaft Removal and Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3406001">Propeller Shaft Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3406002001">
<title>
Removal
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Hoist vehicle.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Before removing propeller shaft, give match marks (1) on joint flange and propeller shaft as shown.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Separate No.2 propeller shaft (2) from rear differential flange.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove No.1 propeller shaft (3) from transfer output flange.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340002.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.119mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "165"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340003.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "55.013mm" ver = "01" gw = "176" gh = "139"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove propeller shaft center bearing support brackets (1) from vehicle body.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Brackets and propeller shaft are removed in one without separation.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Use care not to drop it.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Be careful not to damage boots of joint.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Be careful not to damage oil seal of cross joint.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340004.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.517mm" ver = "01" gw = "207" gh = "135"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
[a]:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Vehicle forward
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3406002002">
<title>
Installation
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3406003">Propeller Shaft Inspection</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3406004">Propeller Shaft Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Reverse removal procedure to install propeller shaft, noting the following point.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
When installing propeller shaft, align the match marks (1). Otherwise, vibration may occur during driving.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Tighten propeller shaft No.1 bolts and center bearing support nuts to specified torque.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<torque>
<torqueitem id = "T3D001">
<t-part>
Propeller shaft No.1 bolt
</t-part>
<t-part1>
a
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
23
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
2.3
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
17.0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
<torqueitem id = "T3D002">
<t-part>
Center bearing support nut
</t-part>
<t-part1>
b
</t-part1>
<t-value1>
50
</t-value1>
<t-value2>
5.1
</t-value2>
<t-value3>
37.0
</t-value3>
</torqueitem>
</torque>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340005.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "55.891mm" ver = "01" gw = "176" gh = "142"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340006.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "64.824mm" ver = "01" gw = "199" gh = "167"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A340007.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.774mm" ver = "01" gw = "207" gh = "147"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "4" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
